cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM

The paper deals with image classification using deep learning techniques, specifically CNN and RNN. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also introduces a novel multi-attention mechanism, which falls under the category of attention-based models, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The paper also involves modeling spatial relationships and defining multiple attention scores, which can be related to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval), respectively. Finally, the paper deals with remote sensing images, which can be related to cs.MM (Multimedia).
